The `Column` (and other positioners for that matter) will not position items that are deemed invisible, the definition being `height` and `width` above zero and `visible = false`. This means you can easily solve it by anchoring the `ListView` to the left and right of it&#39;s parent:

        ListView {
            height:100
            anchors.left: parent.left
            anchors.right: parent.right

            Component.onCompleted: console.log(implicitHeight, implicitWidth)
            model: theModel
            delegate: Text {
                text: display
            }
        }

